### Objective: How to change consent/correct data with low overhead
### Purpose:
#### -Quickly update customer records who withdraw consent
### Solution: 
####  - Store personal data in Apache Hive transaction table where ACID is enabled

msg.data:
Objective: How to change consent/correct data with low overhead

Purpose:

-Quickly update customer records who withdraw consent

Solution:

- Store personal data in Apache Hive transaction table where ACID is enabled

paragraphs.text:
%md
### Consent data
Consent data - whether customer has given consent and consent start dates. This data has been captured by the banks consent management system and available as a Hive table

msg.data:
Consent data

Consent data - whether customer has given consent and consent start dates. This data has been captured by the banks consent management system and available as a Hive table

paragraphs.title: List customers that have given consent for marketing who are located in France
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
select * from consent_master.consent_data_trans where marketingconsent='YES' and country='FR'

paragraphs.title: How many EU ww_customer records in total? (etl_user can see full set of EU records - regardless of consent)
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
SELECT count(*) FROM hortoniabank.ww_customers_trans

paragraphs.title: How many ww_customer records have given consent and consent hasn't expired? (ivanna_eu_hr can only see this set of EU records)
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
SELECT count(*) FROM  hortoniabank.ww_customers where 
    country in (select countrycode from hortoniabank.eu_countries) and 
    insuranceid in (select insuranceid from consent_master.consent_data_trans  where (marketingconsent = 'YES' and current_date < date_add(marketingconsentstartdate, 365)))

paragraphs.title: etl_user can see full set of EU records in www_customers_trans (regardless of consent)
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
SELECT surname, streetaddress, country, age, password, nationalid, ccnumber, mrn, birthday FROM hortoniabank.ww_customers_trans

%md
### What if customer Ostrowski from France wants to withdraw consent given for marketing?
He's tired of all the promotional marketing materials Hortoniabank is sending!

msg.data:
What if customer Ostrowski from France wants to withdraw consent given for marketing?

He's tired of all the promotional marketing materials Hortoniabank is sending!

paragraphs.title: Show consent info for this customer
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
select country, insuranceid, marketingconsent from  consent_master.consent_data_trans where insuranceid='62517316'

paragraphs.title: Update consent info for this customer
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
update  consent_master.consent_data_trans set  marketingconsent='NO' where insuranceid='62517316'

paragraphs.title: Confirm consent was withdrawn
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
select insuranceid,marketingconsent from  consent_master.consent_data_trans where insuranceid='62517316'

-Erasure of individual Records on HDFS/Object stores with fine grained authorization and audit

Solution:

paragraphs.title: Check how many customers have requested data to be erased who do not have any overrides to prevent erasure
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
select count(*)  from hortoniabank.ww_customers_trans w, erasure_master.data_erasure_trans e  where e.insuranceid = w.insuranceid and e.rtbfrequested = 'YES' and e.erasureoverride='NO'

paragraphs.title: Delete data for customers who have requested data to be erased
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
delete from  hortoniabank.ww_customers_trans  where insuranceid in (select w.insuranceid from hortoniabank.ww_customers_trans w, erasure_master.data_erasure_trans e  where ((e.insuranceid = w.insuranceid) and (e.rtbfrequested = 'YES') and (e.erasureoverride='NO')))

SELECT count(*) FROM hortoniabank.ww_customers_trans

###Following cells are to reset ww_customers_trans table after delete

msg.data: Following cells are to reset ww_customers_trans table after delete

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
drop table hortoniabank.ww_customers_trans;

%jdbc(hive_interactive)
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS hortoniabank.ww_customers_trans(
                                    Gender               STRING
                                  , Title                STRING
                                  , GivenName            STRING
                                  , MiddleInitial        STRING
                                  , Surname              STRING
                                  , Number               INT
                                  , NameSet              STRING
                                  , StreetAddress        STRING
                                  , City                 STRING
                                  , State                STRING
                                  , StateFull            STRING
                                  , ZipCode              STRING
                                  , Country              STRING
                                  , CountryFull          STRING
                                  , EmailAddress         STRING
                                  , Username             STRING
                                  , Password             STRING
                                  , TelephoneNumber      STRING
                                  , TelephoneCountryCode INT
                                  , MothersMaiden        STRING
                                  , Birthday             STRING
                                  , Age                  INT
                                  , TropicalZodiac       STRING
                                  , CCType               STRING
                                  , CCNumber             STRING
                                  , CVV2                 STRING
                                  , CCExpires            STRING
                                  , NationalID           STRING
                                  , MRN                  STRING
                                  , InsuranceID          STRING
                                  , EyeColor             STRING
                                  , Occupation           STRING
                                  , Company              STRING
                                  , Vehicle              STRING
                                  , Domain               STRING
                                  , BloodType            STRING
                                  , Weight               DOUBLE
                                  , Height               INT
                                  , Latitude             DOUBLE
                                  , Longitude            DOUBLE
                                )  CLUSTERED BY(Gender) INTO 2 BUCKETS   
                                  STORED AS ORC
                                  LOCATION '/hive_data/hortoniabank/ww_customers_trans'
                                  TBLPROPERTIES ('transactional'='true');
